  7639	        """Detect if task is a duct_flow case via canonical identity.
  7640	
  7641	        P6-TD-002 round-8 correction: use task-name-as-case-identity rather
  7642	        than relying on `hydraulic_diameter` presence alone. Two construction
  7643	        paths exist for TaskSpec and only one normalizes whitelist
  7644	        `parameters` into `boundary_conditions` (src/task_runner.py:232-243);
  7645	        the other (src/knowledge_db.py:60-80) leaves them separate. A
  7646	        name-based primary signal closes the resulting silent-reroute hole.
