   382	        "subtitle": (
   383	            "Visual-only mode (DEC-V61-034 Tier C): real OpenFOAM field + "
   384	            "residual evidence captured; per-case gold-overlay plumbing pending "
   385	            "Phase 7c Sprint 2 (Tier B)."
   386	        ),
